&lt;li&gt;Supported over 350k patients living with obesity across our 5 markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Received selective NICE endorsement to provide services to the NHS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tailored our offering to thousands of patients in Australia, the UK, Germany, Japan and Canada.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;About the Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for an &lt;strong&gt;Analytics Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to own the accuracy, reliability, and scalability of our financial data and reporting, across all of our brands.&lt;/p&gt;
