&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll work closely with the finance and commercial teams for requirements, and the engineering and operations teams globally to shape the data we collect, to produce best in class financial data models. The expectation is full end-to-end ownership: implementation, governance, data quality monitoring, and documentation. We&#39;re scaling across multiple markets, and the rigour of our financial tracking data is directly tied to the quality of decision-making within each markets, and the business’s ability to correctly allocate capital to each market.&lt;/p&gt;
