&lt;p&gt;This role is built for someone who wants &lt;strong&gt;360-degree ownership&lt;/strong&gt; early in their career: someone who&#39;s excited to understand how an entire business works end-to-end through data, not just execute isolated report requests.&lt;/p&gt;
