&lt;li&gt;Use Figma to turn a brief or lo-fi wireframe into a hi-fi design that developers can use to create the experiences in Webflow or Shopify&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create pixel-perfect, intuitive digital experiences that build trust in our healthcare brands, and spark joy for our users&lt;/li&gt;
