&lt;li&gt;Design mobile responsive experiences and consider different user behaviours and experience pathways when it comes to the UX of an experience (error states, cross-sells, logged in vs logged out etc)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Edit (and retouch) images and create icons using Adobe Creative Suite&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to brand design systems for each of our different telehealth brands ensuring it is on-brand&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design digital assets, test, and optimise based on their performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Iterate new designs based on user feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
