&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1tzg99t&quot; data-start=&quot;1677&quot; data-end=&quot;1824&quot;&gt;Enforce expense policies and internal controls by identifying non-compliant spend, resolving discrepancies, and maintaining audit-ready records&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;lwxc4d&quot; data-start=&quot;1825&quot; data-end=&quot;1958&quot;&gt;Serve as the primary point of contact for expense-related queries, providing clear and timely support to employees across markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1foyr4&quot; data-start=&quot;1959&quot; data-end=&quot;2071&quot;&gt;Prepare expense reports and analyses, identifying trends, anomalies, and opportunities for cost optimisation&lt;/li&gt;
